- Introducing the incredibly adorable Minion Hat and Overall short set! This set is fantastic and so versatile - use the hat and overall shorts together, or separate. Pair the overalls with a different hat for a different look. You can even make the overall shorts into pants! This set would make a terrific Halloween costume as well. There is definitely nothing Despicable about this Minion set!

- Great for everyday wear, as a gift or as a photography prop. It's hard to resist these Minion hats!

- This pattern is available in both US and UK Terms.

                                              
{ P A T T E R N - I N F O }
                                              
- Instructions for a beanie in 3 sizes, from Newborn to 12 Months;
- Instructions for adding earflaps and ties;
- Minion Eyes;
- Tongue;
- 3 Styles of Minion Hair;
- Mini-bow to make a girl minion;
- Minion Overall Shorts
- This pattern is suitable for an experienced beginner (familiar with basic stitches).

                                              
