This pattern is suitable for an experienced beginner (familiar with basic stitches). 

The pattern includes the following sizes: 
Newborn, 0 to 3 Months, 3 to 6 Months, 6 to 12 Months, 1 to 4 years, 5 to 12, Teen to Adult, Large Adult

Materials needed:
G (4mm), H (5mm), I (5.5mm) crochet hook
#4 (worsted / medium / 10-ply) yarn
Measuring Tape
Yarn needle

This highly versatile pattern comes with clear & concise instructions to make our own unique Rudolph and Clarisse Reindeer hat. This includes instructions for making:
a beanie hat;
an earflap hat;
Braided and Twisted ties;
Reindeer Snout;
Reindeer Fold-up snout;
Reindeer Nose;
Reindeer Ears;
Reindeer Antlers (mini/baby antlers and "full" antlers);
Reindeer Eyes;
